---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Help - Watch Repair Specialists">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Help Center</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8">
      Welcome to our Help Center. Here you can find answers to common questions and resources to assist you.
    </p>

    <div class="space-y-8">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">How to find a watch repair specialist?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          You can use our search bar on the homepage to enter your city or zip code, or browse by state and city from the "All States" link in the header or the list on the homepage.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">What services do specialists offer?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          Our listed specialists offer a wide range of services including battery replacement, strap repair/replacement, movement overhaul, crystal replacement, polishing, and vintage watch restoration. Specific services vary by specialist.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">How do you rate specialists?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          Specialists are rated based on customer reviews, years of experience, certifications, and the breadth of services they provide. We aim to provide a comprehensive overview to help you make an informed choice.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Can I submit a review for a specialist?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          Currently, we do not have a direct review submission feature on our website. However, we aggregate reviews from various trusted sources to provide a holistic view of each specialist.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mt-12 text-center">Still need help? <a href="/contact" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Contact our support team</a>.</p>
  </main>
</Layout>
